{
  "texts": [
    "The quote extraction stage aims to select only the most relevant quotes from the passages to improve the precision of the answer.",
    "We instruct an LLM to extract verbatim quotes that directly contribute to answering the query (Slobodkin et al., 2024).",
    "As input to the extraction, we gather all passages from the re-ranker for a given paper, and concatenate these to the abstract of the paper.",
    "This aggregation helps create a richer context conducive to extracting relevant quotes.",
    "The LLM processes each paper's content independently and returns the selected quotes separated by ellipses."
  ]
}